Body: The Ivyn project is an ecosystem of everyday products and services where all the users will be able to use several cryptocurrencies as if they were Euros, Dollars, or any other fiat currency. Our users will be able to choose among a growing number of products in the areas of ecommerce, payments, education, trading and investments. Thanks to IvynPay, the main core of Ivyn, each user can choose which currency or cryptocurrency to use for payments. IvynPay is a software suite able to manage electronic money payments in both multi currencies and cryptocurrency. IvynPay will allow all customers to pay with cryptocurrency both within Ivyn and globally
